pre -requrisites
----------------

	-- sudo apt update

	-- sudo apt install openjdk-17-jdk -y
		
		this will install java.
	
	-- sudo apt install maven -y
	
		this will install maven.
		
	-- sudo apt install git -y
		
		this will install git .



1.CLONE THE GIT REPOSITORY.

	-- git clone https://github.com/gokul1638/celcom---java.git

2. move into your project.

	-- cd student_api

3. Mavin build - for jar file generation

	-- mvn clean package
	
	this will create a jar file in the target folder.
	
	 jar file - target/student-api-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar
	
4. start the application

	java -jar target/student-api-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar
